To-Do List App
A simple and responsive To-Do List application to manage your daily tasks efficiently. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this project is perfect for showcasing CRUD operations and DOM manipulation.

Features
📋 Add Tasks: Add new tasks to your to-do list.
✔️ Mark as Completed: Mark tasks as completed with a single click.
✏️ Edit Tasks: Modify existing tasks easily.
❌ Delete Tasks: Remove tasks from your list.
🌙 Dark Mode (Optional): Switch between light and dark themes.
💾 Persistent Storage: Tasks are saved in localStorage and persist after page refresh.
